{"tid":1533211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［整合事件簿］聽日早上7點 光復大埔何郭佩珍中學","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:03:42.000Z","uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16bf67da963fc4049d75ccdf9b72242245f163cb","tid":1533211,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"先講講今日9月2日係何中發生過咩事<strong><em><ins>無興趣既直接去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二樓</span></span>最底</ins></em></strong><br />\n我係大約11點到場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：大約10:30am</ins></span><br />\n收到手足吹雞話<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何郭佩珍中學校長<span style=\"color: orange;\">會交罷課學生名單上教育局</span></span></strong><br />\n因為事關重大所以到場聲援 同時不斷叫人落黎幫手<br />\n到場時間為大約11:00am，只有大約10名手足<br />\n<br />\n<strong>幾件事令我立刻去支援</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.100名罷課學生困係演講廳，學生去廁所有老師帶出帶入<br />\n2.想將罷課學生資料比教育局，清算學生<br />\n3.錄音流出</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：大約11:30am</span></ins><br />\n有<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">議員</span></strong></span>到場幫手話會同校方商量並<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">離去</span></strong> 手足繼續增援同叫口號<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：大約11:50</ins></span><br />\n學生陸續放學，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>但係罷課學生唔係係同一時間放學 而係再遲啲，<span style=\"color: red;\">大約遲幾個字</span></strong></span></span>，然後一位<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>西裝白髮陳先生到場，<span style=\"color: green;\">亦有2名議員</span></strong></span>到場，<strong>向大家解釋點樣可以入校內叫校長出黎面對，學生經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">商量</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">自行評估風險</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（秋後算帳）</span>後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">動用自己權力進入學校要求校長回應，但只有副校長出黎</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：大約02:15pm</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為有手足打算跳樓 </strong> </span></span>，進入左學校既學生翻左出黎。經過眾街坊係下邊大叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">齊上齊落 一個都不能少</span></span>等口號，加上有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>消防員</strong></span></span>過黎幫手，最終獲救並送院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ［手足 如果你睇到個post 希望你唔好再有呢個意圖 我地齊上齊落 一齊相約煲底除口罩好無？應承我地］<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（後記：期間有狗拉左封鎖線，因天雨大風關係吹甩左，然後<span style=\"color: red;\">有2隻狗求期拉左個黑衫手足埋一邊問係咪佢拆既</span>，然後比街坊屌到佢放人，柒下柒下咁汁翻上黎然後再斷過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：大約04:00-05:00pm</ins></span><br />\n選左2位代表，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">前任學生會會長 及 舊生代表</span></strong></span>進入學校同校長<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">談判</span></strong></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">港台記者，西裝陳老師及一名家長陪同</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">以不露面形式去做直播</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（有聲無樣）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：大約0600-0700pm</ins></span><br />\n直播完結，在場人士<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不滿意</strong></span>答案，期間<strong>校長上左私家車開閘打算離開，</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>在場人士 在場人士 在場人士設起左路障</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（好重要要講3次）</span><br />\n就有以下事件發生；<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phJYxXJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphJYxXJ.gif&h=cf1dcbf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後<ins><strong>西裝白髮陳先生試圖調停，</strong></ins>場面一度緊張，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>期間校長車慢慢撞去陳先生到 唔係手足叫住佢真係會碌到陳先生</strong></span></span>，經過一覆爭論後返回校內。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>學生想要爭取五個訴求，但係我唔記得晒 等手足下邊補充</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>1.罷課學生唔要比人秋後算帳<br />\n2.為今朝流出既錄音解釋及道歉<br />\n3.<br />\n4.<br />\n5.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>时间：07:00pm后</ins></span><br />\n学生代表同陈先生入左去同校长<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">谈判</span></strong></span>，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">记者唔准入</span></span>。"},{"pid":"c185ca9ea22e3906b745a01118f3fcfb24459aa3","tid":1533211,"uid":259345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>时间：08:10pm</ins></span><br />\n校长亲自出黎回应诉求，时长大约8分钟。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在场人士唔满意佢只系对录音既用词道歉而唔系因为个意思去道歉</span></span>，因此起哄，<strong>好快就<br />\n有三架狗车到场</strong>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有旗手</span></strong></span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家怀疑校长偷偷报警</span></span></strong>，激起在场人士愤怒。校长经过多翻教训后出闸同狗解释，希望狗收队。经过解释后，班狗出左增援<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>时间：08:32pm</ins></span><br />\n自己睇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>注意 校长已经走左 不理学生安危</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hk3Yx5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHk3Yx5s.jpg&h=0dc7e935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>时间：09:06pm</ins></span><br />\n狗放题<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2RnZLS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2RnZLS.jpg&h=6b258896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>時間：09:10</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>藍旗</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8En2ZMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8En2ZMD.jpg&h=f0cabfef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最後富善街方屌走班狗鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日早上7點 光復何中<br />\n打走仆街校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b01dd92a57d1c7af17856a0b87d03ef89c2a418f","tid":1533211,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"仆街 點解會無啦啦變左殘體字架"},{"pid":"e480a2aef26987d971431265fa49c12d643fc8c7","tid":1533211,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b01dd92a57d1c7af17856a0b87d03ef89c2a418f","tid":1533211,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"仆街 點解會無啦啦變左殘體字架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為你係特別轉黎比支那人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6e10ffa6e0f2b80321d6701fb5336a08fa1fdc","tid":1533211,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e480a2aef26987d971431265fa49c12d643fc8c7","tid":1533211,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b01dd92a57d1c7af17856a0b87d03ef89c2a418f","tid":1533211,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"仆街 點解會無啦啦變左殘體字架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為你係特別轉黎比支那人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"我都唔想 我決定重開,但係我P牌 一日開一POST,所以比FD開,到時幫推"}]}